episodes.title: How Scientology Destroyed A Popular Skateboarding Channel
episodes.description:
Braille Skateboarding was once an unstoppable skateboarding channel, who suffered possibly the strangest downfall in YouTube history. At the centre of everything seemed to be a weird reliance on scientology, which heavily contributed to the channel's eventual fall. What went wrong?

This is, How Scientology Destroyed A Popular Skateboarding Channel

Thank you guys for watching, like and sub if you enjoyed, SunnyV2

Also, the idea for this video was inspired by "Dumb Data" who posted a video on a similar topic in January 2024 titled "Aaron Kyro, and the Rise and Fall of Braille Skateboarding's YouTube Channel" You can watch his version here - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V-GIyKIlL9g&t=672s
